Release Notes 0.7
=================

XDI3Segment -> XDIAddress
XDI3SubSegment -> XDIArc
XDI3Statement -> XDIStatement

String xdiEndpointUri = xdiDiscoveryResult.getXdiEndpointUri();
->
URL xdiEndpointUrl = xdiDiscoveryResult.getXdiEndpointUrl();

in many methods "Xri" -> XDIAddress or XDIArc
e.g. Message.setLinkContractXri() -> Message.setLinkContractXDIAddress() 

changed constant names
XRI_S_ -> XDI_ADD_
XRI_SS_ -> XDI_ARC_

slightly different exceptions in xdi2.client
Xdi2DiscoveryException, Xdi2ClientException

XdiLocalRoot -> XdiCommonRoot

contributorXris -> contributorAddresses

